reviewText: It was not what i was expecting, it's like a little summary of their lives and present show at the time it was made.  Less than half an hour, i was expecting more of the shows.
Two masters of their trade who portray their talent in an exciting and dangerous act. Your eyes won't stray from the screen for a minute.
I had been looking for a DVD like this off and on for years, and it is just what I was hoping for, maybe more. It combines the guys' backgrounds and their accomplishments beautifully.

I purchased this as a gift for someone who had seen them perform in Vegas, and they loved this collection. The Seller sent the product in great condition, and I had it in no time at all. There was nothing negative about this gift giving experience.
